      <div class="msgContentFrame">It is a very hard class to level but i love playing with it.  <br />1. It takes twice as long to level this class as any other and i have multiple toons at diffrent levels and i was able to go into other zones alot sooner then glad. <br />2.Provoke either aoe or solo is just so under powered,plus if you have a Mard in the group  <br />they just take all hate right away. Now i can control the hate but its three times more difficult then any other game i have ever played. <br />3.It seems at the lower levels Mard is best suited to tank is this going to be the new tank class. <br />4.Why does glad attack so low and miss so frequent? <br />5.Will there be a update to address the glad under powered stats, to me it seems that people get to a certain rank right now for glad and then just give up because of this ? <br /> <br />thanks for listening Se <br />  <br /> <br /></div>
