      <div class="msgContentFrame">You apparently are doing it wrong as we've had 3 people in our linkshell ditch a Pugilist, Marauder and Lancer so far claiming that they enjoy the GLA more and he gets better skill up. Oddly enough, it only took them a few days to catch up to their &quot;mains&quot; rank. <br /> <br />Obviously knowledge of the game + physical level helped with the quicker ranking but bottom line is they had zero issues with getting rank as a GLA. And on that note often times I'd duo with the GLA as a CON in like Mun Tuy Cellars and they would beg me to go back because they were getting such great skill. <br /> <br />If anything right now, as far as our LS is concerned the GLA seems better than most the other melee classes. He does comparable damage, can take hits much better, has more HP, keeps mobs off the casters, etc. etc. We now have 4 GLA in the LS and when we get 6-7 of us together it rocks having all the GLA and as a CON I get great skill up healing them all day long!</div>
