      <div class="msgContentFrame">t takes twice as long to level this class as any other and i have multiple toons at diffrent levels and i was able to go into other zones alot sooner then glad.  <br /> <br />Well, i can tell you FOR SURE why this is the case because i did some testing/ watching. <br />Mar/LNC/PUG tanks level faster because they dont have a shield. <br /> <br />Example. You are a GLD and you are tanking. A monster tries to hit you and hits your shield. You get x amount of shield exp and maybe some hp back or something else if you have shield skills...  <br /> <br />NOW, if you are one of the other classes. A monster tries to hit you and you parry. You get WEAPON sp. If you are in a group and up hunting you can get ALOT of SP just off of parries. The higher level the monster is the more chance to get SP off of parries.  <br />And if you are looking at MAR who has steadfast which increases parry chance and foresight to boot, you are looking at a lot of parry chances which is alot of chances for sp gain. <br /> <br />The moral of the story is, if you want alot of sp tanking is a good way to go. If you want the most sp, go MAR.  <br /> <br />(the above is to be taken as my opinion and not a statement of fact in any way.)</div>
